    {
      "id": "rec-001",
      "courseId": "course-001",
      "studentId": "student-1",
      "body": "Based on your performance in the Binary Search Tree quiz, I recommend reviewing Self-Balancing Trees (AVL). You struggled with rotation logic—would you like me to generate a visual step-by-step guide for Left-Right rotations?",
